	<Title>
		Food allergy: Can it develop later in life?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Food allergies usually occur during childhood &amp;mdash; but they can appear at any age.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Can adults develop a food allergy?
	</Question>
